<!-- ================================ DESCRIPTION  -->

    <refsect1 id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            Atomically sets the value pointed to by 
            <varname>object</varname> to true. Memory is 
            affected according to the 
            value of <varname>order</varname>. These 
            operations are atomic read-modify-write operations (as defined by 
            section 5.1.2.4 of the C11 specification). 
            Returns atomically, the value of the object immediately 
            before the effects.
        </para>

        &atomicFunctionsInc;

    </refsect1>

